{"tid":1373373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[抗爭報告] 有關於每一次出去發完夢之後點撤退既建議","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T04:57:04.000Z","uid":130797,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e53ad9c6060fc874a6c4467116dc292144ca3d6e","tid":1373373,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:18:34.000Z","msg":"我係元朗live po度講過下面既建議<br />\n有巴打建議我另外開po講<br />\n希望大家睇一睇 再想一想<br />\n<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n先多謝今日企前線既兄弟<br />\n而我就係大家口中所講既膽小懦夫<br />\n<br />\n入正題<br />\n我見到每一場抗爭都重複緊一個問題<br />\n就係幾時撤退<br />\n而所謂「撤退時機」<br />\n其實多數係同「勝利條件」有關<br />\n<br />\n我明白前線巴打有勇有謀<br />\n企得出黎 擊退警犬 士氣好 當然唔會放過勝利既機會<br />\n但究竟每一場抗爭既勝利條件係咩?<br />\n我就好清楚警犬個邊既勝利條件就捉鳩哂大家<br />\n<br />\n有時候<br />\n唔係前線巴打戀戰<br />\n亦都未必係後場巴打淆底走得快<br />\n而係前線 和理非 冷氣軍師心入面想達成既事唔統一<br />\n和理非同軍師可能覺得警犬出煙彈已經係達成目標可以走<br />\n但前線巴既要求理所當然會更高<br />\n<br />\n以今日元朗一役為例<br />\n勝利條件係咩?<br />\n如果事前無一個清晰具體既目標<br />\n後場可能會太早走<br />\n前線就太遲走<br />\n明明大家都係為件事好 但結果唔知點解會變成互屌<br />\n<br />\n試想想<br />\n如果今日一戰前線已經定左個目標 (當然呢個都係一件困難既事)<br />\n我舉個例子<br />\n例如話大家要衝入去元警入面佔領快閃既<br />\n和理非可能未必同意兄弟咁做<br />\n但我地既然應承過無條件支持<br />\n咁就一定會支持到前線達成個條件<br />\n亦都知道左達成目標就會一齊走<br />\n以上呢個例子係七一入立會就好好體現左出黎<br />\n<br />\n所以我既提議係<br />\n下次前線既有咩目標想達成既<br />\n請具體表達俾後場知道<br />\n有時聽到兄弟話後面無人support 真係好心酸<br />\n其實支持你地既人唔會少<br />\n亦都非常關心你地既安危<br />\n但良好溝通 就可以避免左互相猜疑所帶黎既不安<br />\n<br />\n天佑香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b0f72fb3af32f604668ddd35250c91c9b70b42","tid":1373373,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:21:40.000Z","msg":"推一推<br />\n兄弟們既裝備同思想一直升緊級<br />\n當然圍內既溝通都需要升級啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea92772372a4caa93c0c49284f36bc2e8c50ffe5","tid":1373373,"uid":10997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:25:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b349acca98e8efac6eab752888dec4053441c96","tid":1373373,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:25:41.000Z","msg":"係時候成立民間防衛隊做返警察應該做嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n依家咁多證據都證明<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">警察=黑社會</span></span>，依家嘅警察已經失去合法性<br />\n<br />\n首先可以由集體唔交稅開始<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E7XMWCx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE7XMWCx.png&h=73fa9ee1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06647c32393f9bb1b19d446a57ff88395c56b38c","tid":1373373,"uid":263098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:25:44.000Z","msg":"幫手推<br />\n<br />\n勇武和理非 缺一不可"},{"pid":"1b41820a9842406c550e69668baf08aa51408c5f","tid":1373373,"uid":59668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:25:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"089984d58a2c8f75231ca70d9e1a41eb348c0fdd","tid":1373373,"uid":14274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:26:34.000Z","msg":"push support"},{"pid":"7fc7afe29e861a6f96842f1c8c6ca29598010dba","tid":1373373,"uid":130797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:27:35.000Z","msg":"其實警犬已經暴走到呢個點<br />\n以後既活動入面<br />\n前線巴只要唔係話用燒村殺人做目標<br />\n我諗後場都會好多人支持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059803157e4634100c511565c417342ea36881af","tid":1373373,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:29:24.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n<br />\nagree"},{"pid":"aa170a6124bdc8ea55b144c7541451c223ba41a3","tid":1373373,"uid":263098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:31:18.000Z","msg":"其實冷氣軍師犬一出就幫手整佈防圖<br />\n後排mon tg早d通知前排<br />\n前排下決定<br />\nwork唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過前綫風頭火勢食住煙得唔得閒討論去留係問題"},{"pid":"24c90a75194a35430a9b93de5dd4cb9763b70524","tid":1373373,"uid":14274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:32:59.000Z","msg":"討論下先<br />\n<br />\n勝利條件好難幾日前傾緊<br />\neg 幾日前開定目標係估總嘅，對面實報佈晒防，難度又高咗<br />\n<br />\n如果即日對侍嗰陣睇情形決定，跟住要搵方法傳俾後排聽support"},{"pid":"4f35a093c347c75a15d3560d991926c0b548efcd","tid":1373373,"uid":74287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:34:44.000Z","msg":"同意 幫手推"},{"pid":"2aa88d917777afb5e1e7a8b77d670387409ebe20","tid":1373373,"uid":263098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:34:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如唔好話前線幾點會撤<br />\n<br />\n試下前線走去後面話會死守到幾點<br />\n我地後排、物資站一定企足<br />\n死線前15分鐘再講話撒定繼續死守到幾點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直播post(3) #1876 見到<br />\n搬埋過黎集思廣益下"},{"pid":"e085e9dad034e5eb26d1336fc2cecf6df7b1a859","tid":1373373,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:36:10.000Z","msg":"當然我都有提及到<br />\n「決定目標」都可能已經係一件好困難既事<br />\n仲記得呢個星期大家已經為<br />\n1. 主唔主動出手<br />\n2. 入唔入村<br />\n3. 甚至幾點去元朗<br />\n都講到耳赤紅面<br />\n<br />\n所以我都只係提出一個最理想既狀況<br />\n但都希望大家會向呢個狀況去思考每一場運動既策略<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1acd0b6931bc65830d7bf5ef380df599b196257e","tid":1373373,"uid":263098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:37:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8af9b998a1560c3630a8ce77624e26d2e219acf3","tid":1373373,"uid":265949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:37:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02f12fb8fb3adb6a4f3c599978cf9322dbf81d64","tid":1373373,"uid":23854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:41:21.000Z","msg":"推 係個好法子"},{"pid":"8a884fa29af854d068bd9d844de409dba7edc16d","tid":1373373,"uid":23854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"有呢d目標就唔洗咁依賴現場溝通"},{"pid":"698cf9ffb94d2c77c3a67b1ac85bfc1d61c7529a","tid":1373373,"uid":290198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:43:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c2cb3660cf2730ea4f9d29d34cca8552e2bbf505","tid":1373373,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:45:59.000Z","msg":"一路話入夜前撤退, 如果前線想留守係咪應該比D訊息其他人?"},{"pid":"56fc01c21b27f2a2c9450b36d0f956ab37761438","tid":1373373,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a884fa29af854d068bd9d844de409dba7edc16d","tid":1373373,"uid":23854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"有呢d目標就唔洗咁依賴現場溝通"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:46:09.000Z","msg":"當然<br />\n現場瞬息萬變<br />\n警犬又一直mon po<br />\n即場改變目標 我相信都將會係常態<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8524ecd95fefec7d4b12cfefc37845e2767cda","tid":1373373,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2cb3660cf2730ea4f9d29d34cca8552e2bbf505","tid":1373373,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:45:59.000Z","msg":"一路話入夜前撤退, 如果前線想留守係咪應該比D訊息其他人?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:49:15.000Z","msg":"巴打<br />\n呢個就係我想講因為溝通不良而帶黎既不安<br />\n<br />\n我非常相信前線巴打係本住被捕被打而行前<br />\n心態上 唔想咁輕易就撤都係好正常<br />\n只係大家唔align返個計劃<br />\n後面既人 就唔知道需要支持前線到幾多點<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d7a63519e2512e3a31a13f56ed9117d3ce0f44","tid":1373373,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:50:18.000Z","msg":"打排球前排有手勢<br />\n<br />\n參考下"},{"pid":"bb81bda6f311521bebe41af1a4ceca8483baca42","tid":1373373,"uid":161504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:01:46.000Z","msg":"Push!!!"},{"pid":"22cd1033717c456d7a818999903d1857ab4b86f7","tid":1373373,"uid":189453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:28:42.000Z","msg":"只要有實際性 客觀嘅目的 其實好多嘢都唔使煩<br />\n727係對721元朗警方嘅不滿 [表達要追究警方嘅責任]<br />\n但係呢個係一個好主觀嘅目的 係一個訴求 <br />\n點樣先叫追究咗 好難定義<br />\n引用隔離post所講<br />\n點解今次撤離容易留人難<br />\n好多人將責任放係 冷氣軍師到<br />\n但真正原因係 撤離 係一個好客觀嘅 <br />\n好實際嘅目的 就係走 <br />\n但係留低嘅目的係乜 問題又返點樣先叫追究咗警方責任"}]}